			<div class="col-12 col-md-10 offset-md-1">
				<h1 class="text-center mb-xs-2 color-white">&#8216;Music à La Mode&#8217;</h1>
				<div class="author text-center dek color-light-blue font-giza">
										


<a href="https://www.nybooks.com/contributors/lawrence-kramer/" class="dek color-light-blue font-giza hover-border-light-blue hover-text-light-blue text-decoration-none"><span class="dek color-light-blue font-giza hover-border-light-blue hover-text-light-blue text-decoration-none"><strong>Lawrence Kramer</strong></span></a>, reply by <a href="https://www.nybooks.com/contributors/charles-rosen/" class="dek color-light-blue font-giza hover-border-light-blue hover-text-light-blue text-decoration-none"><span class="dek color-light-blue font-giza hover-border-light-blue hover-text-light-blue text-decoration-none"><strong>Charles Rosen</strong></span></a>				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-12 col-md-10 offset-md-1 col-lg-6 offset-lg-3 color-white">
									<div class="mt-xs-6"></div>
